OL,3,CDriver, 83, killed ex-police officer
OL,4,Cafter suffering leg spasm
OL,6,FAn elderly driver who killed a retired
OL,7,Fpolice officer after losing control of
OL,8,Fhis car following a leg spasm has
OL,9,Favoided being jailed.
OL,11,FChristopher Pattinson, 83, mounted the
OL,12,Fpavement and collided with 80-year-old
OL,13,FStuart McPherson on Belmont Wharfe
OL,14,Fbridge, Skipton, on 22 March 2023.
OL,16,FMr McPherson, of Horbury, Wakefield,
OL,17,Fdied from multiple injuries. His wife,
OL,18,FMarjorie, was also knocked down and
OL,19,Finjured but survived.
