OL,6,FTwo other pedestrians had to pin
OL,7,Fthemselves to the bridge wall to avoid
OL,8,Fbeing hit.
OL,10,FPattinson pleaded guilty to causing
OL,11,Fdeath by dangerous driving.
OL,13,FBradford Crown Court heard he had
OL,14,Fsuffered a leg spasm due to a medical
OL,15,Fcondition and accelerated into Mr and
OL,16,FMrs McPherson.
OL,18,FHe was given a two-year prison
OL,19,Fsentence, suspended for two years and
OL,20,Fbanned from driving for life.
