OL,6,FIn a victim personal statement, Mrs
OL,7,FMcPherson said her husband of 56 years
OL,8,Fwas "kind, caring, loving and
OL,9,Fdedicated to his family".
OL,11,FShe added: "His death was untimely and
OL,12,Ftragic, and our greatest sorrow is
OL,13,Fthat we were not able to say goodbye
OL,14,Fto him. This has had a great effect on
OL,15,Fall our lives, particularly mine, as I
OL,16,Fwas present at the scene of the
OL,17,Faccident and was unable to be by his
OL,18,Fside when he died. He is still always
OL,19,Fon my mind."
