OL,6,FDet Con Laura Cleary, of North
OL,7,FYorkshire Police, said: "This was an
OL,8,Fabsolutely tragic and needless death
OL,9,Fthat has devastated a family. It
OL,10,Fhighlights the need for everyone to
OL,11,Fensure they are fit to drive before
OL,12,Fgetting behind the wheel ` regardless
OL,13,Fof their age.
OL,15,F"If you do have a medical condition,
OL,16,Fplease check whether you must disclose
OL,17,Fit to the DVLA, including any changes
OL,18,Fin that condition."
